stions! </span><a href=\"mailto:cbgraf@gwmail.gwu.edu\"><span style=\"color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">cbgraf@gwmail.gwu.edu</span></span></a></div>\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">-Christie</span></div>\n\";s:10:\"field_id_5\";s:1:\"y\";s:11:\"field_id_30\";s:10:\"GW Blogger\";s:11:\"field_id_19\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"field_id_20\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"entry_date\";i:1339104653;s:15:\"expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;s:3:\"395\";i:1;s:3:\"351\";}s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"open\";s:11:\"new_channel\";s:1:\"1\";s:6:\"author\";s:1:\"1\";s:18:\"versioning_enabled\";s:1:\"y\";s:6:\"submit\";s:6:\"Submit\";}'),
	(32,350,1,2,1347050791,'a:19:{s:8:\"entry_id\";s:3:\"350\";s:10:\"channel_id\";s:1:\"1\";s:17:\"autosave_entry_id\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"filter\";s:80:\"YToyOntzOjEwOiJjaGFubmVsX2lkIjtzOjE6IjEiO3M6Njoic3RhdHVzIjtzOjY6ImNsb3NlZCI7fQ==\";s:5:\"title\";s:23:\"1st Ever Georgey Awards\";s:9:\"url_title\";s:23:\"1st-ever-georgey-awards\";s:10:\"field_id_2\";s:7449:\"<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: left;\">\n	<span font-size:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\">So you know how professional sports have an award show named the ESPY&rsquo;s? Well, this year GW decided to host their own version, honoring the best of GW athletics. And so, everyone in the athletic department, including the athletes, coaches, administration, and academic support donned their best semi-formal attire and traveled over to GW&rsquo;s Lisner Auditorium for an evening of fun. </span></div>\n<p>\n	<span font-size:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span><br />\n	<span font-size:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\">It was strange seeing all of the other athletes dressed up in dresses and suits because you rarely see them dressed in something other than athletic clothing. Everyone looked wonderful and the evening was rather enjoyable. It started off around 6:00pm with pictures outside, followed by appetizers in the lobby and basement of Lisner. Finally, at 7:00pm, the main event of the night began. The awards show was hosted by a member of the women&rsquo;s soccer team and a member of the men&rsquo;s baseball team. The awards being given ranged from Mr. and Miss Colonial and Community Service Award to <span style=\"color: #222222;\">Colonials&#39; Best Moment of the Year. </span>My volleyball team and I were actually nominated for the Colonial Best Moment of the Year for our phenomenal comeback and victory versus Georgetown in the DC Challenge, but ultimately lost to <span style=\"color: #222222;\">Men&#39;s Golf for setting a scoring record to earn their program&#39;s first-ever A-10 Championship. </span></span><br />\n	<br />\n	<span font-size:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\"><span font-size:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \" times=\"\">Those who planned it put a lot of effort into it and it paid off. The event was a hit and we all can&rsquo;t wait until next year&rsquo;s cere</span></span></span><span font-size:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"font-family: \" times=\"\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\"><span font-size:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \" times=\"\">mony. And of course, I have some pictures from the evening. <o:p></o:p></span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n				<a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-PG7E8OTB74E/T8LB77Ga07I/AAAAAAAACNc/ivM6lvKdFvs/s1600/spring+2012+129.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-PG7E8OTB74E/T8LB77Ga07I/AAAAAAAACNc/ivM6lvKdFvs/s320/spring+2012+129.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n				GW Volleyball Team (I am in the front row on the far left)</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n				<a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-A1fhjNNqEtE/T8LCB75z82I/AAAAAAAACNs/cybXfVnaOdA/s1600/spring+2012+130.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"205\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-A1fhjNNqEtE/T8LCB75z82I/AAAAAAAACNs/cybXfVnaOdA/s320/spring+2012+130.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n				Roommates!</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n	<a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-EDTBp5aTEGI/T8LCMOMH5cI/AAAAAAAACN0/kIS11INW1HY/s1600/spring+2012+132.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"248\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-EDTBp5aTEGI/T8LCMOMH5cI/AAAAAAAACN0/kIS11INW1HY/s320/spring+2012+132.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n				<a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VYNArKB3_cw/T8LBmoIAw_I/AAAAAAAACNE/6ca5zzkQ0QQ/s1600/spring+2012+439.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-VYNArKB3_cw/T8LBmoIAw_I/AAAAAAAACNE/6ca5zzkQ0QQ/s320/spring+2012+439.jpg\" width=\"216\" /></a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n				Georgey Award Statue *photo courtesy of gwsports.com</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n				<a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wfCxhvKjVBU/T8LBvDt3SVI/AAAAAAAACNM/QD3z-DABhY4/s1600/spring+2012+440.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"204\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wfCxhvKjVBU/T8LBvDt3SVI/AAAAAAAACNM/QD3z-DABhY4/s320/spring+2